Brazil Investigating Possible Mundial Stock Price Manipulation

-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 
2011-09-15T01:23:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/brazil-investigating-possible-mundial-stock-price-manipulation.html
Brazilian police and regulators are
searching the headquarters of Mundial SA Produtos de Consumo
after a local court issued search warrants to investigate the
possible manipulation of the company’s stock price.  The warrants and investigation were announced in an e-
mailed statement from  Brazil ’s securities regulator. The
company’s headquarters are located in Porto Alegre, Brazil.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lucia Kassai in Sao Paulo at 
 lkassai@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jonathan Roeder at 
 jroeder@bloomberg.net  